&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;wiki_link_ext&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_ato2007-2010/2010/lei/l12305.htm&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_ato2007-2010/2010/lei/l12305.htm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;[3] 1o Semin&amp;aacute;rio Estadual de Lixo Eletr&amp;ocirc;nico do Estado do Cear&amp;aacute; -&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;wiki_link_ext&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; href=&quot;http://ce-waste.net/palestras.html&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://ce-waste.net/palestras.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-text field-field-situacao-conectaz&quot;&gt;
